title: Ep#7 - STFU
itunes:title: Ep#7 - STFU
itunes:subtitle: Megan wakes up trapped in the bathroom after what she believes was an earthquake. When her cries for help are answered by a horrifying sound she doesn’t recognize, she realizes she should have stayed silent.
description:
Megan wakes up trapped in the bathroom after what she believes was an earthquake.
